</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios';

export default {
  data() {
    return {
      items:[]
    }
  },


  created() {
    axios.get(`https://zbeta2.mykuwaitnet.net/backend/en/api/v2/media-center/press-release/?page_size=61&type=5`)


    .then(response => {
     
      this.items = response.data
    })
    
  }
}

</script>
